ck TungTough™ samples are delivered to NRC and Innotech Alberta for wear and impact tests', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '324-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-04-14 14:15:10', '2025-04-14 06:15:10', '', 324, 'http://localhost:70/?p=326', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (327, 1, '2025-04-14 14:31:25', '2025-04-14 06:31:25', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"viewer-foo\">We had a fantastic time at MINExpo 2024 in Las Vegas! It was a great opportunity to meet so many industry professionals, showcase our advanced materials, and discuss innovative solutions for the mining industry. The turnout was incredible, and we are grateful to everyone who stopped by our booth!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"viewer-0zfba95\">Special thanks to all the attendees who engaged with us and took interest in our Titanium Carbide (TiC) + Chrome White Iron (CWI), Sintered TiC, Crack-Free CCO, and PTAWCO Technology. Your insights and enthusiasm inspire us to keep pushing the boundaries of wear protection.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"viewer-nszar97\">Stay tuned - we\'ll be sharing more updates and exciting projects soon.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":316} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"http://localhost:70/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2ca1e9_1dc89f8c33f94358a9fe1c8485fa47d8mv2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-316\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":315} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"http://localhost:70/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2ca1e9_b3d5135b3b434ea4bd26f06eae069077mv2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-315\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->', 'Amazing Experience at MINExpo 2024', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '314-autosave-v1', '', '', '2025-04-14 14:31:25', '2025-04-14 06:31:25', '', 314, 'http://localhost:70/?p=327', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (328, 1, '2025-04-17 05:05:00', '2025-04-16 21:05:00', '<h3 class=\"font_3 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Composite polymer ceramic coating</span></h3>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">CIM developed a polymer-based ceramic coating for corrosive and erosive services. Hard ceramic particles SiC, AI</span><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">2</span><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">O</span><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">3, </span><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Si</span><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">O</span><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">2, </span><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">or Si</span><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">3</span><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">N</span><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">4</span><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"> were combined with the polymer, and the bonding strength could get above 15 MPa.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"font_3 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">corundum ceramic coating</span></h3>\r\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Corundum ceramic coating is made from 2600 ̊C molten alumina (AI</span><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">2</span><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">O</span><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">3</span><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">) centrifugally formed inside the steel pipe wall. The hardness of corundum ceramic coating is above 90 HRC, and it has excellent wear resistance, corrosion resistance and thermal shock resistance.  </span></p>', 'COATING', 'Composite polymer ceramic coating\r\nCIM has developed a polymer-based ceramic coating designed for corrosive and erosive applications. This advanced coating combines hard ceramic particles such as SiC, Al₂O₃, SiO₂, or Si₃N₄ with a durable polymer matrix, achieving a bonding strength of over 15 MPa. This innovative solution offers enhanced protection in demanding environments, ensuring superior performance and longevity.\r\n\r\n​\r\n\r\ncorundum ceramic coating\r\nThe Corundum Ceramic Coating is created by centrifugally forming 2600°C molten alumina (Al₂O₃) inside the steel pipe wall. With a hardness exceeding 90 HRC, this coating offers exceptional wear, corrosion, and thermal shock resistance, making it ideal for demanding industrial applications.  ', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '294-autosave-v1', '', '', '2025-04-17 05:05:00', '2025-04-16 21:05:00', '', 294, 'http://localhost:70/?p=328', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
